<div id="review_635281348" class="review nosyndicate" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/635281348" />
    <a title="Ron" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/1256262-ron"><img alt="Ron" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1442983573p2/1256262.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/635281348?book_show_action=true">Jun 07, 2013</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Ron" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Ron" href="/user/show/1256262-ron">Ron</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780986843716" href="/book/show/13559482-the-time-weaver">review of another edition</a>


        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1256262-ron?shelf=young">young</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1256262-ron?shelf=ebook">ebook</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1256262-ron?shelf=fantasy">fantasy</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer635281348" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer4097183927194009964">Another hundred page burnout.<br/><br/>A failed beginners attempt at epic fantasy. All the right elements were there--obviously so--but the story is too wooden and predictable and the story telling is sophomoric. (I was tempted to list the apparent sources of many of the elements, but don&apos;t want to waste anymore time on this story. The reader will have no trouble picking them out.)<br/><br/>An interesting parallel worlds premise, but the author betrays complete ignorance about how the military and governments work.</span>
  <span id="freeText4097183927194009964" style="display:none">Another hundred page burnout.<br /><br />A failed beginners attempt at epic fantasy. All the right elements were there--obviously so--but the story is too wooden and predictable and the story telling is sophomoric. (I was tempted to list the apparent sources of many of the elements, but don't want to waste anymore time on this story. The reader will have no trouble picking them out.)<br /><br />An interesting parallel worlds premise, but the author betrays complete ignorance about how the military and governments work. Given the emotional state of most of the principle characters, this story must be aimed at young readers. If I were a teen, I think I'd be insulted.<br /><br />Don't waste your time.</span>
  <a data-text-id="4097183927194009964" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

<tr class="no_border feedFooterReview" id="update_comment_stuff_Review635281348">
  <td colspan="2">
    <div class="updateActionLinks">
        <a class="right flag" rel="nofollow" id="flag_link635281348" title="Flag this review as inappropriate." href="/flagged/new?resource_id=635281348&amp;resource_type=Review&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13037859-the-time-weaver">flag</a>





      <span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_review_635281348'><a id="like_count_review_635281348" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/635281348?resource_type=Review"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it gr-button gr-button--small" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F13037859-the-time-weaver">Like</a></span>
&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a href="/review/show/635281348?book_show_action=true&amp;from_review_page=1">see review</a>
    </div>


    <div id='comments_for_review_635281348' style='display: none;'>
