              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9898969247192541220">I won this book with good reads first reads so first off thanks. I really enjoyed this book, I don&apos;t tend to read too many fantasy book but this one pulls you in from the first page. Really good definitely going to read the next one.</span>
  <span id="freeText9898969247192541220" style="display:none">I won this book with good reads first reads so first off thanks. I really enjoyed this book, I don't tend to read too many fantasy book but this one pulls you in from the first page. Really good definitely going to read the next one.</span>
