<div id="review_1751228749" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/1751228749" />
    <a title="Alysha Filer" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/16669393-alysha-filer"><img alt="Alysha Filer" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1358805834p2/16669393.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/1751228749?book_show_action=true">Sep 07, 2016</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Alysha Filer" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Alysha Filer" href="/user/show/16669393-alysha-filer">Alysha Filer</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Paperback 9780986843716" href="/book/show/13559482-the-time-weaver">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1751228749" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13189282539623939151">This book is great! The characters are well developed and I enjoyed their stories and adventures. I&apos;m not huge on fight scenes, so some of those scenes are a bit long for me - but they&apos;re written well and the detail is phenomenal - enough to give you the picture, not enough that he is repeating himself or focusing too much on one fight.<br/><br/>I often find books to be a spin off of others, or a mix of others... that was not the case here! TAK uses the elements in a really unique manner. I was continuall</span>
  <span id="freeText13189282539623939151" style="display:none">This book is great! The characters are well developed and I enjoyed their stories and adventures. I'm not huge on fight scenes, so some of those scenes are a bit long for me - but they're written well and the detail is phenomenal - enough to give you the picture, not enough that he is repeating himself or focusing too much on one fight.<br /><br />I often find books to be a spin off of others, or a mix of others... that was not the case here! TAK uses the elements in a really unique manner. I was continually learning and enjoying each chapter!</span>
  <a data-text-id="13189282539623939151" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

