<li class='cover' id='bookCover_34914739'>
<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/34914739-i-am-watching-you"><img alt="I Am Watching You" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1503335237l/34914739._SX98_.jpg" />
